			<div class="question">Question 1: Tell us something about yourself.(include your placed co.)</div>

			<div class="answer">Answer:My name is Shashwat Shaurya. I used to be a college student before someone ate a bat(or pangolin). Currently, I am interning at Paytm. My roller-coster started at BIT Mesra in 2017 as a student of Chemical(Plastic&Polymer) branch. I believed in myself. I studied well and managed to change my branch to Electronics and Communication Engineering (which most of my friends said I shouldn't have). I had an interest in robotics and in the first year itself I was included in Robolution as an intern. This gave me an identity of being cool and nerdy at the same time. Towards the second year, I had developed interest in Web Development too and hence started exploring it. But my journey at Robolution and Team Pratyunmis continued. I was inducted into the team as a mechanical subtem member but post my branch change I started to work with embedded subteam as well. I tried to keep a balance between my studies, responsibilities(here at Robolution) and my friends. This often reduced my sleeping hours- for this I have been referred to as a zombie. I also used to watch a lot of TV Series- I often forget some while counting. But I am happy that I was able to fill in every second of my life at BIT with some memory.</div>
