			<div class="answer">Answer:My projects were on Web Development- MERN techstack. I had done a QrCode based over the web file transfer application. A chat application. I had developed website for IEEE- student's chapter BIT, Mesra. I had built a gesture operated warehouse forklift robot. The other projects that I did with Robolution were team efforts.
			I also got an oppotunity to intern at IIT Delhi on SLAM of Autonomous Vehicle for their DLive project. There I worked with lot of modern hardware and technologies including Lidars, Jetson GPU boards, ROS. I got to learn a lot. There I even volunteered in organizing the nationals of ABU-ROBOCON as we knew the knooks and crooks of the play. Overall it was a great experience.
